{"tid":904020,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世文]  做過HKUE 你問我答","createTime":"2018-11-16T04:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T19:39:00.000Z","uid":207225,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7207957e9671ff9a7d92940a69e164ed8ea906","tid":904020,"uid":207225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"見到之前指南針開左個POST 而且DSE差唔多準備到 為左防止DSE小朋友受害 <br />\n有關呢間野 只要我知 一定答你 <br />\n所有資料基本上係問番曾經的受害者同畢業生<br />\n唔答有關自己的問題<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n以下有關資料有助理解本貼及幫助DSE雞唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n[自資學位]做過指南針大學，你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/217760/page/25?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/217760/page/25?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上網找了一些有關HKUE澳洲升學資料，希望幫到中六學生<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bcRskS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bcRskS</a><br />\n<br />\n［回帶］DSE雞必睇！借屍還魂！HKUE傳銷殺入教育界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/KhjtS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/KhjtS</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">曾經好像有相關的貼文，但最後好像因為收到律師信被要求刪除，若發生相同情况希望各位巴絲友做好backup準備，當幫助下DSE雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"519561d005ab0868ee457b6d2c0efd95535ca838","tid":904020,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b6099a03289d643f0eb3be3a3e4e8a3c84e1d4","tid":904020,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:24:42.000Z","ms